===============================
vue-remote-component Change Log
===============================

.. current developments

v1.4.1
====================

**Fixed:**

* Upgrade dependencies for latest security fixes.



v1.4.0
====================

**Added:**

* Added `integrity` attribute for [subresource
  integrity](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Subresource_Integrity)
  checks when loading code from untrusted sources.



v1.3.1
====================

**Fixed:**

* Cleaned up `tag` interface.



v1.3.0
====================

**Added:**

* Show a spinner while the component is loading. Show an error indicator when loading failed.



v1.2.0
====================

**Added:**

* Props to remote component can now be provided as by their original name as expected. Except for props named `url`, `extract`, `props` and `name` which must still be passed as e.g. `:props={name: "value-of-name"}`.



v1.1.0
====================

**Added:**

* support RequireJS pages



v1.0.3
====================



